## Getting Started

### Prerequisites

{% if values.language == 'nodejs' -%}
- Node.js 18+
- npm or yarn
{% elif values.language == 'python' -%}
- Python 3.11+
- pip
{% elif values.language == 'go' -%}
- Go 1.21+
{% endif -%}

### Environment Variables

{% if values.resourceType == 'database' -%}
```bash
DATABASE_HOST={{ values.name }}-db
DATABASE_PORT=5432
DATABASE_NAME={{ values.name }}
DATABASE_USER=<from-secret>
DATABASE_PASSWORD=<from-secret>
```
{% elif values.resourceType == 'bucket' -%}
```bash
GCS_BUCKET_NAME={{ values.name }}
```
{% endif -%}

### Installation

{% if values.language == 'nodejs' -%}
```bash
